hopobject.body: Will I have to work shifts? st anthony pharmacy east grand avenue el segundo ca There are always a few commenters in stories like this who insist that the Surface RT is a great product at any price. I’ll take the charitable view that these folks aren’t crazy, and I’ll allow that Surface RT makes sense in a handful of specific circumstances. Namely, if all you need in a tablet is a web browser and maybe a handful of basic apps like Netflix, and if full Office compatibility is essential for getting work done, then maybe the Surface RT handles all your needs for under $500.
